*'''''Crossfire'' 02B Munitioner''' (2010)
  +
:An unlicensed transforming figure and accessory upgrade kit by [[FansProject]] for the ''Universe''/''Revenge of the Fallen'' Bruticus Maximus combiner set. The "Munitioner" figure is a modern redesign of Swindle, which transforms into a [[Humvee]]. Accessories in the package include a large rifle, redesigned head, waist, forearm, hands and foot for Bruticus.<ref>[http://www.tfw2005.com/transformers-news/universe-classics-20-29/images-of-fansproject-crossfire-sets-combined-form-and-weapons-169120/ TFW2005.com - Images of FansProject Crossfire Sets, Combined Form and Weapons]</ref>
